column2: SELECT d.dr7ObjID, s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, gs.D4#_N_SUB, gl.H_ALPHA_FLUX, gl.H_ALPHA_FLUX_ERR, gl.H_BETA_FLUX, gl.H_BETA_FLUX_ERR, gl.OIII_#_FLUX, gl.OIII_#_FLUX_ERR, gl.NII_#_FLUX, gl.OI_#_FLUX, gl.OI_#_FLUX_ERR, gl.NII_#_FLUX_ERR, ge.lgm_tot_p5#, ge.sfr_tot_p5#, ge.lgm_fib_p5#, ge.sfr_fib_p5#, gi.sn_median, gl.sigma_balmer, gl.H_ALPHA_EQW, gl.oii_#_flux, gl.oii_#_flux_err, gl.oii_#_flux, gl.oii_#_flux_err, gi.v_disp, gi.v_disp_err, ge.bptclass ph.petroR5#_r, ph.petroR9#_r from SpecObj as s into mydb.sdss_o2ratio_sample JOIN photoobjall as ph on s.bestObjID = ph.objID JOIN galSpecIndx as gs on s.specObjID = gs.specObjID JOIN galSpecInfo as gi on s.specObjID = gi.specObjID JOIN galSpecLine as gl on s.specObjID = gl.specObjID JOIN galSpecExtra as ge on s.specObjID = ge.specObjID JOIN wISE_xmatch as wg on s.bestObjID = wg.sdss_objid JOIN wISE_allsky as ws on ws.cntr = wg.wise_cntr INNER JOIN specDR7 as d on d.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE s.z BETWEEN # AND #
